I"º<h3 id="start-in-4-steps">Start in 4 steps</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Download or clone repo <code>git clone git@github.com:nandomoreirame/simplest.git</code></li>
  <li>Enter the folder: <code>cd simplest/</code></li>
  <li>Install bundle gem: <code>gem install bundle</code></li>
  <li>Install local gems: <code>bundle install</code></li>
  <li>Start Jekyll server: <code>jekyll serve</code></li>
</ol>

<p>Access, <a href="http://localhost:4000/simplest">localhost:4000/simplest</a></p>

